---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'February 25, 2026';
---
<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy — TechMo Electronics"
  description="Learn how TechMo uses cookies and tracking technologies on its website."
  canonical="/cookies"
>
  <Navbar />

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e3a8a] text-white py-14 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">🍪</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-custom">
      <div class="notice-box">
        <strong>Short version:</strong> TechMo's website uses minimal cookies. Our analytics tool
        (Cloudflare Web Analytics) is cookie-free and GDPR-compliant. We do not track you across
        other websites.
      </div>

      <section aria-labelledby="c1">
        <h2 id="c1">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help
        websites remember your preferences, keep you logged in, and understand how you use the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c2">
        <h2 id="c2">2. What Cookies Does TechMo Use?</h2>

        <div class="cookie-table-wrap">
          <table class="cookie-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Cookie / Technology</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Purpose</th>
                <th>Duration</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><code>cf_clearance</code></td>
                <td>Security</td>
                <td>Cloudflare bot/DDoS challenge verification</td>
                <td>Session / 30 days</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Cloudflare Turnstile</td>
                <td>Security</td>
                <td>CAPTCHA-free bot protection on forms</td>
                <td>Session</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Cloudflare Web Analytics</td>
                <td>Analytics</td>
                <td>Cookie-free, privacy-first site analytics (no personal data)</td>
                <td>No cookie stored</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4">We do <strong>not</strong> use:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Google Analytics or any Google tracking</li>
          <li>Facebook Pixel or social media tracking</li>
          <li>Advertising cookies or cross-site trackers</li>
          <li>Third-party retargeting cookies</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c3">
        <h2 id="c3">3. Essential Cookies</h2>
        <p>Some cookies are strictly necessary for our website and services to function correctly.
        These cannot be disabled without affecting core functionality. They include security tokens
        set by Cloudflare to protect our infrastructure from bots and attacks.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c4">
        <h2 id="c4">4. Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> to understand how visitors use our site.
        This tool is:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cookie-free</strong> — no cookie is placed on your device</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy-first</strong> — no personal data is collected or stored</li>
          <li><strong>GDPR-compliant</strong> — no consent required under EU law</li>
          <li>Data is aggregated and anonymised; individual visitors are never identified</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c5">
        <h2 id="c5">5. Your Choices</h2>
        <p>Because we use very few cookies — and none for advertising — there is little to configure.
        However, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use your <strong>browser settings</strong> to block or delete cookies</li>
          <li>Use a <strong>browser extension</strong> such as uBlock Origin to block tracking scripts</li>
          <li>Enable <strong>Do Not Track</strong> in your browser — we honour this signal</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Blocking security cookies (cf_clearance) may prevent you from accessing our website
        if Cloudflare detects unusual traffic from your network.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c6">
        <h2 id="c6">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Cookie Policy if we add new technologies to our site. The "last updated"
        date at the top of this page will reflect any changes.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="c7">
        <h2 id="c7">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about our use of cookies? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:privacy@techmo.lk">privacy@techmo.lk</a> or visit our
        <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="policy-link">Privacy Policy →</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="policy-link">Terms of Service →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom { @apply text-[#334155] leading-relaxed; }
  .prose-custom h2 { @apply text-xl font-bold text-[#0f172a] mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100; }
  .prose-custom p { @apply mb-4 text-[15px]; }
  .prose-custom ul { @apply list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 mb-4 text-[15px]; }
  .prose-custom a { @apply text-[#1e40af] hover:underline font-medium; }
  .prose-custom strong { @apply text-[#0f172a]; }
  .notice-box { @apply bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 text-sm text-[#334155]; }
  .policy-link { @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-[#1e40af] hover:text-[#1e3a8a] transition-colors; }
  .cookie-table-wrap { @apply overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-100 mt-4; }
  .cookie-table { @apply w-full text-sm; }
  .cookie-table th { @apply bg-[#f8fafc] px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wide; }
  .cookie-table td { @apply px-4 py-3 border-t border-gray-50 text-[#334155]; }
  .cookie-table tr:hover td { @apply bg-[#f8fafc]; }
  .cookie-table code { @apply bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono text-slate-700; }
</style>
